.:: Zebra puzzle ::.
Color: red, green, ivory, yellow, blue
Food: apple, asparagus, mango, zucchini, cauliflower
Flower: lily, iris, bellflower, sunflower, begonia
Beverage: coffee, tea, milk, orange-juice, water
Pet: dog, fox, zebra, horse, snails

1. Food:apple == Color:red
2. Food:asparagus == Pet:dog
3. Beverage:coffee == Color:green
4. Food:mango == Beverage:tea
5. Color:green is to the right of Color:ivory
6. Flower:lily == Pet:snails
7. Flower:iris == Color:yellow
8. Beverage:milk is in the middle
9. Food:zucchini is on the far left
10. Flower:bellflower is on the left or right of Pet:fox
11. Flower:iris is to the left or right of Pet:horse
12. Flower:sunflower == Beverage:orange-juice
13. Food:cauliflower == Flower:begonia
14. Food:zucchini is to the left or right of Color:blue

.:: Answer ::.
|		|       1	|	2	|	3 	|	4	|	5	|
| Food	|   zucchini	|    mango	|     apple	|    asparagus	|    cauliflower	|
| Color		|    yellow	|      blue	|      red	|     ivory	|     green	|
| Beverage	|     water	|      tea	|      milk	| orange-juice	|     coffee	|
| Flower		|     iris	| chesterfield	|    olg-gold	| sunflower	|   parliament	|
| Pet		|     fox	|     horse	|     snails	|     dog	|     zebra	|
